::KitKat::

She semi woke up in the CR and looked around.  She kew she was in the 
CR, but didn't know how she got there.  She was still feeling a 
little numb, but was regaining her strength back.  She closed her 
eyes and fell asleep.

She dreamed of watching Land Mine.  She saw her being held by the 
maximals.  She cried out in her sleep,"NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!"
She watched herself take up her rifle and shoot Land Mine.  She cried 
in her sleep, "I'm sorry, I'm sorry."

She fell into a deeper and quieter sleep.
